NAME
    pod2slide - convert POD to slide show

SYNOPSYS

      perl pod2slide.pl myslideshow.pod

REQUIREMENTS
    pod2slide requires the following modules:

      Pod::POM
      HTML::Template

DESCRIPTION
    This program converts a POD file to a slide show presentation.

    Each page in the slide show is identified by a =head1 tag.

    It was written as an alternative to Mark Jason Dominus'
    "txt2slides" <http://perl.plover.com/yak/txt2slides.tgz>
    utility.

AUTHOR
    Robert Rothenberg <rrwo at cpan.org>

